title: MockLocationService - remove .self
message:
MockLocationService - remove .self

Always bind to MockLocationService instead of using .selfInitialized and
.self (remove) - this way always use android synchronization mechanisms to
verify the service is running instead of inventing our own.

ForegroundService has been updated to bind to MockLocationService
instead of using MockLocationService.self - note calling
unbindService(this) from onServiceConnected callback - hope that's save
even in older android versions.

title: GeoFixCommand added. MockLocationProvider added. Notifications removed.
message:
GeoFixCommand added. MockLocationProvider added. Notifications removed.

Notifications removed because we can't guaranteed using current android APIs they will be consistent with the actual state (running/stopped) of the service. Eg. it might easily happen that MockGeoFix application gets killed but the notificatin states on.

MockLocationProvider and supporting code added. GeoFixCommand added.
GeoCommand bugfix.
Mock locations relative checks added to MainActivity.
